{"tid":2277543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［改名撐Trump] 一個簡單支持Trump嘅方法","createTime":"2020-11-08T13:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:44:59.000Z","uid":156109,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"506ddb379fb252d885c4877ffe508f09471146ae","tid":2277543,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"由於有啲鬼佬上到連登以為呢度啲人係撐Biden<br />\n甚至喺某啲左膠擅自代表香港人係奚落 Trump<br />\n所以喺度邀請大家用最簡單嘅方法 <br />\n令其他人知道Hong Kongers Stand with Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參加方法：<br />\n喺名前面/後面加（MAGA) 再轉做紅字<br />\n<br />\n例如我叫 陳大文<br />\n就變做<span class=\"red\">（MAGA)陳大文</span><br />\n記得轉做紅字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除咗改名 仲可以上 Trump 網站課金支持佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.donaldjtrump.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donaldjtrump.com&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq77QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=02221dd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.donaldjtrump.com</a><br />\n<br />\n👆上去課金，Trump 有個&rdquo;We Need to Fight Back&rdquo; 網站，快！要Trump 幫香港，香港人都要撐返佢！<br />\n<br />\n大把court case 嚟緊，Trump 唔放棄，我哋都唔好放棄！"},{"pid":"1d49239d18af01c793c2e7636a822c4854bd3f1f","tid":2277543,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27928147453185b1db525c5989908b391245552","tid":2277543,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9825a31e0c1e61e7b6632088297619818493b0c","tid":2277543,"uid":34872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"Maga maga fire"},{"pid":"ebd9884f49a42d0e3bc217a108191aa6472eedd3","tid":2277543,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />